ed="T" n="0841a21"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0841a21"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date>廣州羅浮山<persName key="A012742">道行</persName>傳</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0841a22"/><persName key="A012742">釋道行</persName>，姓梅氏，<placeName key="PL000000013240">會稽</placeName>人也。父為<placeName key="PL000000013239">越州</placeName>衙吏。<lb
ed="T" n="0841a23"/><persName key="A012742">行</persName><date key="j19986441999009" from-iso="+0760-01-01" to-iso="+0760-12-31">弱齡</date>知書，比成造秀。有僧分衛，<persName key="A012742">行</persName>接之<lb
ed="T" n="0841a24"/>談道，頗精禪觀，遂求出家。至四明山<placeName key="PL000000012326">保壽<lb
ed="T" n="0841a25"/>院</placeName><persName key="A012746">智幽</persName>所，稟訓進修，拾薪汲水。後遊<placeName key="PL000000028928">南岳</placeName>，<lb
ed="T" n="0841a26"/>聞<persName key="A003623">江西大寂</persName>道化，往親附焉。思養聖胎，見<lb
ed="T" n="0841a27"/><placeName key="PL000000031276">羅浮</placeName>奇異，高三千丈，有七十石室，七十二長<lb
ed="T" n="0841a28"/>溪。仙人仙禽，玉樹朱草，生于上，半入海中。<lb
ed="T" n="0841a29"/><persName key="A012742">行</persName>居于石室，默爾安禪。然或山精水怪，往往<pb ed="T" n="0841b" xml:id="T50.2061.0841b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0841b01"/>驚鳴，<persName key="A012742">行</persName>視之蔑如也。有老人容貌端正，衣<lb
ed="T" n="0841b02"/>冠華楚，再拜稽顙云：「我居此中僅二百載，<lb
ed="T" n="0841b03"/>今因<persName key="A012742">師</persName>住，冥感匪躬，逍遙脫苦，歸人趣受<lb
ed="T" n="0841b04"/>樂矣。」其感物多此類也。<date from-iso="+0825-02-02" key="j20224182023128" to-iso="+0827-01-13">寶<anchor xml:id="beg0841sgsz3"/>曆<anchor xml:id="end0841sgsz3"/>九載</date>疾終<!--寶曆沒有九年，這裡依（疑年錄：134）標為寶曆年間-->，春<lb
ed="T" n="0841b05"/>秋九十五。<date key="j20230492023049" when-iso="+0826-10-26">其年九月十八日</date>入塔焉。</p>
